Based on the ranking criterion of **Monthly Active Users** and the available market research, here are the 20 most prominent apps for searching offers and deals on items, ranked by estimated or reported audience size and industry influence. Note that not all of these apps publicly disclose exact monthly active user counts, but their ordering reflects industry trends, app analytics data, and third-party research on reach and popularity in the coupon, cashback, and deals sectors[2][4][1].

